Description:
fopen function that avoids clobbering std{in,out,err}.

Files:
lib/stdio--.h
lib/stdio-safer.h
lib/fopen-safer.c
m4/stdio-safer.m4

Depends-on:
fopen
unistd-safer

configure.ac:
gl_FOPEN_SAFER
gl_MODULE_INDICATOR([fopen-safer])

Makefile.am:

Include:
"stdio-safer.h"

